# First 9 bars of the first "Saw" track from a locally-stored MIDI file.
# Format: <note> <duration_ms> per line. Note is e.g. C4, Gs4, As3
# (s = sharp, b = flat); R is a rest. Blank lines and '# ...' comments
# are ignored. At 120 BPM 4/4, one bar = 2000 ms, one eighth = 125 ms.
#
# The 9th bar in the source is a silent bar (trailing R 2000); keeping
# it makes the loop breathe naturally before restarting.

